{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require online games have child-only servers to help protect children",
        "additional_details": "There is a huge problem with grooming via online gaming and action is needed to create a safer way for children to play games online.\r\n \r\nWe believe that requiring child-only servers, with rigorous age and ID checks, would better protect children from online dangers.\r\n",
        "background": "Bring in a law that gaming companies hosting online games need to provide child-only servers for UK users, with access limited to under 16s. The Government should require ID and age checks to ensure these servers are only used by children.",
